  "title": "Lava Turns Sand into Glass",
  "description": "When Lava Touches Sand Blocks They Turn into Glass Blocks",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Dn7NvW.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lava-turns-sand-into-glass-fabric-forge\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/883465?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lava-turns-sand-into-glass\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/lava-turns-sand-into-glass?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This configurable mod makes Sand blocks instantly transform into Glass upon contact with lava. Perfect for creating glass farms or just adding a fun touch to your gameplay. &nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DXY3iwp.png\" width=\"524\" /></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/lavasand.json</code> in your profile folder.</p>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>blocks_to_glass</b> - List of blocks that lava turns into glass</p></center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>\n",
